<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{HeaderTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Nunito', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .code-block { background-color: #272822; color: #f8f8f2; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.12);">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #704294 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #c5468e 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; opacity: 0.1; font-size: 120px; line-height: 1;">üìß</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">{{HeaderTitle}}</h1>
            <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.95; position: relative; z-index: 1;">Your Application is Ready for Email Integration</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div style="padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.8; color: #495057;">
            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello <span style="color: #704294; font-weight: 700;">{{AppOwner}}</span>,</p>

            <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Congratulations! Your application <strong style="color: #704294;">{{AppName}}</strong> has been successfully registered with TPMailer and is ready for deployment.</p>

            <!-- Success Badge -->
            <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #f1f8f6 100%); border: 1px solid #a5d6a7; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; border-radius: 8px;">
                <div style="color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">‚úì Application Configured</div>
                <div style="color: #558b2f; font-size: 14px;">Your application <strong>{{AppName}}</strong> is now fully configured and ready for email integration.</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Credentials Section -->
            <h3 style="color: #704294; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px;">üìã Application Credentials</h3>

            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf8ff 0%, #f5f3ff 100%); border-left: 4px solid #704294; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px;">
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-weight: 600; width: 180px; color: #704294;">Application Name:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; color: #333;">{{AppName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">App Client ID:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;"><span style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 700;">{{AppClientId}}</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">App Secret:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;"><span style="color: #d63384; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(214, 51, 132, 0.1); padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px;">{{AppSecret}}</span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">From Email Address:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; color: #333;">{{FromEmailAddress}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">SMTP Type:</td>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0; color: #333;">{{SmtpType}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <!-- Managed SMTP Badge -->
            <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #f1f8f6 100%); border: 1px solid #a5d6a7; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; border-radius: 8px;">
                <div style="color: #2e7d32; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px;">‚úì TP Services (Managed SMTP)</div>
                <div style="color: #558b2f; font-size: 14px;">Your application uses managed SMTP credentials. You don't need to provide AppPassword in API calls - credentials are automatically managed by our system.</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick Start Guide -->
            <h3 style="color: #704294; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px;">üöÄ Quick Start Guide</h3>

            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <h4 style="color: #704294; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Step 1: Authentication</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #495057;">Obtain a JWT token using your App Client ID and App Secret:</p>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #704294; font-size: 13px;">HTTP Request</div>
            <div class="code-block">
POST {{BaseUrl}}/api/AppUser/ApplicationAuthentication
api-version: 1.0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "AppClientId": "{{AppClientId}}",
  "AppSecret": "{{AppSecret}}"
}
            </div>

            <p style="color: #495057;"><strong style="color: #704294;">Response:</strong> You'll receive a JWT token. Use this token in the Authorization header for all subsequent requests.</p>


            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <h4 style="color: #704294; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">Step 2: Send Email</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: #495057;">Use the JWT token to send emails via our API:</p>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: #704294; font-size: 13px;">cURL Example</div>
            <div class="code-block">
curl -X POST "{{BaseUrl}}/api/EmailService/SendEmail" \
  -H "api-version: 1.0" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN" \
  -F "Subject=Your Email Subject" \
  -F "Body=&lt;p&gt;Your HTML email content here&lt;/p&gt;" \
  -F "IsHtml=true" \
  -F "ToRecipients=recipient@example.com" \
  -F "CcRecipients=cc@example.com" \
  -F "attachment=&#64;/path/to/file.pdf"
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;">Paste your JWT token in the Authorization header before sending the request.</div>

            <!-- Required Fields -->
            <h4 style="color: #704294; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 12px;">üìù Required Fields</h4>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #faf8ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <ul style="padding-left: 25px; line-height: 2; color: #495057; margin: 0;">
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Subject</strong> - Email subject line</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">ToRecipients</strong> - Semicolon-separated email addresses</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">IsHtml</strong> - Set to <code style="background: rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;">true</code> for HTML emails</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Optional Fields -->
            <h4 style="color: #704294; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 12px;">üìé Optional Fields</h4>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #faf8ff 0%, #ffffff 100%); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <ul style="padding-left: 25px; line-height: 2; color: #495057; margin: 0;">
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">Body</strong> - Email body content (HTML or plain text)</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">CcRecipients</strong> - Semicolon-separated CC email addresses</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #704294;">attachment</strong> - File attachments (use multiple <code style="background: rgba(112, 66, 148, 0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;">-F</code> parameters)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6c757d;">If you need any assistance or have questions, our support team is ready to help.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Best regards,<br><strong style="color: #704294;">TPMailer Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f7ff 0%, #faf8ff 100%); padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #704294;">TPMailer</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">&copy; {{Year}} All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #c0c4cc;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
